Instructions for developers who use the source code repository
**************************************************************

SVN repository
==============

Initial checkout:

svn co svn+ssh://YOUR_LOGIN@svn.isr.lanl.gov/n/svn/LanlGeoMag/trunk LanlGeoMag
cd LanlGeoMag

Later updates:

svn update

Committing your work:

svn commit


Compiling
=========

Just once (or just occasionally):

autoreconf -i
./configure

Every time:

make
